flowRoot.flowPara: This is your new sweet-ass dialog for making calendar events. Right now you only have the basics, a box to name the event and some smaller boxes to control when its taking place.

As you type, it will try to assign an icon to your event so that its easier to remember later. Additional details you type in here like where the event will be and who will be with you will automatically be filled out. You can also choose which calendar this event will be saved in at this step.

text.tspan: Mega movie marathon in Silver City with Me

flowRoot.flowPara: After that, you can add or remove fields on your own using the icons at the bottom. When editing these fields, relevant things will show, like a calendar when you're changing the date.
